Blaze.uk.description: ...Henry and Sam's Wreck-trospective. Henry and Sam visit the Classic Motor Show in Birmingham. (S1, ep 10)

Blaze.uk.description: Mystery Safe: Rick and Chum try to sniff out deals for Superman pyjamas and a vintage industrial slicer. Also, a helmet signed by Mario Andretti find its way into the shop.

Blaze.uk.title: Container Wars
Blaze.uk.description: Blow a Casket: The Israelis form an unexpected alliance that threatens to bury their competition. (S1, ep 13)

Blaze.uk.description: Blowing Smoke: When a container with a shady past lands on the auction block, Mo and Ty prepare themselves to go all in. (S1, ep 14)

Blaze.uk.title: Container Wars
Blaze.uk.description: Cargo Contraband-O: The competition approaches fever pitch when a container from south of the border lands at the Port of Los Angeles. (S1, ep 15)

Blaze.uk.title: Container Wars
Blaze.uk.description: Lost at Sea: The biggest auction on the planet sails to the middle of the Pacific Ocean when a mysterious container is dredged up from the bottom of the sea. (S1, ep 16)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Hunters
Blaze.uk.description: Lock and Load: T-Money wins a mysterious bin with a massive, chained-up steel door. (S3, ep 3)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Hunters
Blaze.uk.description: Bling and Bang: The big tension of the day is between T-Money and Brandon. T goes for the mystery bins - the box and the barrels. (S3, ep 4)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Hunters
Blaze.uk.description: Winter Wonderland: A trip to Lake Arrowhead brings rain, snow and a new couple who drive Brandori crazy. (S3, ep 5)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Hunters
Blaze.uk.description: Out with the Old: The new couple, the "younger, trendier Brandon and Lori" are back. (S3, ep 6)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas
Blaze.uk.description: Puffy The Auction Slayer: Ricky's mother Puffy, a veteran of storage locker battles, makes waves as she joins the bidding for abandoned treasures in upscale Haslet. (S6, ep 14)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas
Blaze.uk.description: For The Benefit Of Mr. Charles: Jenny attempts a bold new strategy at Longview auctions that prove full of surprises. Mary shows up with a mystery friend. (S6, ep 15)

Blaze.uk.title: Storage Wars Texas
Blaze.uk.description: Moe's Def: The auction season ends with a record-breaking sale in Fort Worth. Limited to one locker a year by his wife, hoarder Moe shows up to make his annual purchase. (S6, ep 16)

Blaze.uk.title: History's Greatest Mysteries

Blaze.uk.title: The Curse Of Oak Island
Blaze.uk.description: On Target: After months of hard work, the Laginas once again descend the Garden Shaft and finally hit the tunnel they've been chasing all year. (S11, ep 15)

Blaze.uk.description: Alton City Escape: Quawntay gets caught in a marijuana bust and sentenced to prison - but when he learns he is going to be a father, he determines to escape. (S2, ep 6)

Blaze.uk.title: New: Discovered By Disaster
Blaze.uk.description: Explore evidence that ties a meteor strike to a Biblical tale. Delve into a treasure-filled tunnel revealed by a sinkhole in Mexico. (S1, ep 4)

Blaze.uk.description: Satan Comes to Salem: An inexplicable evil torments the young girls of Reverend Samuel Parris' household before spreading through Salem. The afflicted make witchcraft accusations. (1 of 4)

Film4.uk.title: Boston Strangler
Film4.uk.description: (2023) Keira Knightley stars as Loretta McLaughlin, the reporter who fought 60s chauvinism to break the story of the notorious titular serial killer, in Matt Ruskin's true crime procedural.

Film4.uk.title: She Said
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Fact-based drama with Zoe Kazan and Carey Mulligan. New York Times journalists Jodi Kantor and Megan Twohey investigate the sexual abuses of Hollywood producer Harvey Weinstein.

Film4.uk.title: French Exit
Film4.uk.description: (2020) Comedy drama with Michelle Pfeiffer. A skint Manhattan socialite moves to Paris with her son and a cat... which may or may not contain the spirit of her dead husband.

Film4.uk.title: The Sound Barrier
Film4.uk.description: (1952) Drama starring Ralph Richardson as a pioneering aviator determined to break the sound barrier, even if it means risking the lives of those closest to him. Directed by David Lean.

Film4.uk.title: Gideon of Scotland Yard
Film4.uk.description: (1958) Drama. Jack Hawkins stars as Police Inspector Gideon, who faces outrage and danger in his quest to bring London's criminals to justice. With Anna Massey, John Loder and Cyril Cusack.

Film4.uk.title: Animal Farm
Film4.uk.description: (1954) George Orwell's cautionary tale reimagined in cartoon form. A farm's animals revolt against their abusive owner only for the pigs to become drunk with their newly found power.

Film4.uk.title: Footsteps in the Fog
Film4.uk.description: (1955) Atmospheric Victorian melodrama. Stewart Granger plays a sinister aristocrat who poisons his wife. However, his maid (Jean Simmons) knows his secret and tries to use it against him.

Film4.uk.title: Legends of the Fall
Film4.uk.description: (1994) Oscar-winning turn-of-the-century drama with Brad Pitt and Anthony Hopkins. A Montana patriarch's son falls for his brother's fiance, setting off a tragic chain of events.

Film4.uk.title: American Gangster Special
Film4.uk.description: Denzel Washington, Russell Crowe and director Ridley Scott talk about making American Gangster, the 2007 crime epic based on an unlikely true story.

Film4.uk.title: American Gangster
Film4.uk.description: (2007) True crime thriller directed by Ridley Scott. An outcast New York cop (Russell Crowe) is charged with bringing down entrepreneurial Harlem drug lord Frank Lucas (Denzel Washington).

Film4.uk.title: The Mechanic
Film4.uk.description: (2011) Thriller with Jason Statham and Donald Sutherland. A hitman is ordered to kill his mentor, but then takes on the dead man's son as an apprentice. Could get complicated... and deadly.

Film4.uk.title: A Quiet Place Part II
Film4.uk.description: (2020) Hushed-horror sequel with Emily Blunt and Cillian Murphy. Armed only with a hearing aid, can the family evade the vicious aliens with super-hearing, and find a community to live in?

Film4.uk.description: (2019) Animated adventure featuring the voices of Jennifer Garner, Mila Kunis, John Oliver and Matthew Broderick. A girl's imaginary theme park comes to life when her mum goes to hospital.

Film4.uk.title: Spies in Disguise
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Animated spy comedy caper with the voice of Will Smith. The 'world's most awesome spy' gets framed and has to go undercover as a pigeon to prove his innocence.

Film4.uk.title: The Desert Fox
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Drama. James Mason stars in Henry Hathaway's sympathetic portrait of Field Marshal Erwin Rommel in the final years of his life during the Second World War. With Jessica Tandy.

Film4.uk.title: The Perfect Catch
Film4.uk.description: (2005) Comedy. Ben (Jimmy Fallon) must choose between his two loves: Lindsey (Drew Barrymore) and the Boston Red Sox baseball team. Based on Nick Hornby's novel Fever Pitch.

Film4.uk.title: The Day After Tomorrow
Film4.uk.description: (2004) Tense sci-fi thriller starring Jake Gyllenhaal and Dennis Quaid. A scientist sets out to save his son when global warming plunges the world into a sudden climatic catastrophe.

Film4.uk.title: The King's Man
Film4.uk.description: (2021) The spy-caper franchise continues with the origins story of the Kingsman agency, as a plucky group battle an international conspiracy at the outbreak of WWI. With Ralph Fiennes.

Film4.uk.title: Scream
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Meta-comedy horror 're-quel' with Courteney Cox. Killer Ghostface returns to shock the younger generation out of their love of 'elevated horror' with a bit of old-fashioned slashing.

Film4.uk.title: Dead of Night
Film4.uk.description: (1945) Five uncanny tales of the supernatural in one eerie package, the most famous starring ventriloquist Michael Redgrave and a deadly dummy. Prepare to be spooked.
